      "content": "but that's the thing, why would i want to reach out? that's just more effort, more noise. everything is just so loud and heavy. if i just quietly left, it wouldn't disrupt anything. no one would have to deal with my sadness or my problems. it seems like the only way to actually find some quiet is to just stop trying to exist in a world that doesn't even see me. wouldn't it be more compassionate to just let someone go if they aren't really there anyway?",
